director.name: 托尔斯坦·比约克朗德 Torstein Bjørklund

introduction: The story follows a group of high school friends in the heart of Sápmi, Karasjok. It’s about friendship, struggles, love, and what happens when an accusation of rape changes everything. The NRK series in pre-production, has received co-financing from Yle. It is supported by the International Sámi Film Institute, the Norwegian Film Institute, Film Fund North, the Audio and Visual Fund Norway and Bergesenstiftelsen. The premiere is set for November 2024.
